! Settings

!! Engine Selection

Select the graph engine in the tw-graph plugin settings:

''ControlPanel > Settings > Graph Engine > Cytoscape''

Or set the config tiddler directly:

|!Tiddler |`$:/config/flibbles/graph/engine` |
|!Value |`Cytoscape` |

!! Compound Node Styling

Compound (parent) nodes use a semi-transparent background with rounded rectangle shape by default. To customize, override the `node:parent` selector in the Cytoscape stylesheet via graph-level properties.
